This is a project that aims to speed up the process of checking in and retrieving a coat at a coat check service.

For the font to appear larger in the UI, you need to add the following to this file: 
"C:\Python27\Lib\site-packages\gtk-2.0\runtime\etc\gtk-2.0\gtkrc"

style "font"
{
font_name = "Arial 20"
}
widget_class "*" style "font"
gtk-font-name = "Arial 20"